<h3> Deleting stashed changes</h3>

```
$ git stash list
    stash@{0}: On master: change to mission page title

$ git stash drop stash@{0}
Dropped stash@{0} (3cf1456f525559767f871b49bbcf7e7d3752dd46)

# ### delete everything in the stash
$ git stash clear
```